title: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems
description: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems this is inred text.
OB: Upon choosing the project name 'test,' a static text validation error appears on the 'Copy Project' dialog.
EB: The static text validation error should not appear when selecting the project name 'test.'
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Create a single project with the name 'test'.
2. Copy and paste the project.
3. In the 'Copy Project' dialog:
   a. Ensure that the 'Use Default Location' option is checked.
   b. You should still be able to select or copy the default location from the edit box below.
   c. Allow choosing a path close to the default location if desired.
